---
import SendIcon from "../icons/SendIcon.astro";
---

<h2 class="text-3xl text-white font-semibold text-center mt-4 lg:text-5xl">
  Contactanos
</h2>
<div class="mt-4 px-12 lg:mt-8">
  <form action="" class="mx-auto max-w-xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-1 lg:gap-y-4">
      <div>
        <label
          for="first-name"
          class="block text-xs md:text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white"
          >Nombre</label
        >
        <input
          type="text"
          name="first-name"
          id="first-name"
          autocomplete="given-name"
          placeholder="Carlos"
          class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border-0 px-3 py-3 text-xs md:text-sm text-white font-medium bg-gray-100/50 shadow-sm shadow-blue-500 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-300 placeholder:text-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-blue-400"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label
          for="last-name"
          class="block text-xs md:text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white"
          >Apellido</label
        >
        <input
          type="text"
          name="last-name"
          id="last-name"
          autocomplete="family-name"
          placeholder="Arnulfo"
          class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border-0 px-3 py-3 text-xs md:text-sm text-white font-medium bg-gray-100/50 shadow-sm shadow-blue-500 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-300 placeholder:text-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-blue-400"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <label
          for="email"
          class="block text-xs md:text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white"
          >Email</label
        >
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          id="email"
          autocomplete="email"
          placeholder="carlosarnulfo@gmail.com"
          class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border-0 px-3 py-3 text-xs md:text-sm text-white font-medium bg-gray-100/50 shadow-sm shadow-blue-500 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-300 placeholder:text-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-blue-400"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <label
          for="phone-number"
          class="block text-xs md:text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white"
          >Telefono</label
        >
        <input
          type="tel"
          name="phone-number"
          id="phone-number"
          autocomplete="tel"
          placeholder="77888 - 9955"
          class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border-0 px-3 py-3 text-xs md:text-sm text-white font-medium bg-gray-100/50 shadow-sm shadow-blue-500 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-300 placeholder:text-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-blue-400"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <label
          for="message"
          class="block text-xs md:text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white"
          >Mensaje</label
        >
        <textarea
          name="message"
          id="message"
          rows="4"
          placeholder="Aqui coloca una breve descripcion de tu consulta..."
          class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border-0 px-3 py-3 text-xs md:text-sm text-white font-medium bg-gray-100/50 shadow-sm shadow-blue-500 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-300 placeholder:text-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-blue-400"
        ></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-2 px-2 md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-white text-xs lg:text-sm">
          Al enviar esta información, aceptas nuestros <span
            class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-md"
            >términos y condiciones</span
          > y nuestra <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-md"
            >política de privacidad</span
          >, donde explicamos cómo recopilamos y utilizamos tu información.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center md:col-span-2">
        <button
          class="rounded-lg relative w-40 h-10 cursor-pointer flex items-center border border-green-400 bg-blue-600 group hover:bg-blue-600 active:bg-blue-500 active:border-green-600"
        >
          <span
            class="text-white font-semibold ml-8 transform group-hover:translate-x-20 transition-all duration-300"
            >Enviar</span
          >
          <span
            class="absolute right-0 h-full w-10 rounded-md bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center transform group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <SendIcon class="Size-20 text-white" />
          </span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
